# TaskLyst — Cursor IDE Context File

**Purpose:**
This file provides a concise, structured context for Cursor IDE to load as project context / system prompt / reference for an LLM-powered assistant while developing **TaskLyst** — a web-based task management system with an LLM-powered intelligent assistant for task prioritization and predictive scheduling, utilizing **Livewire 3 components** for interactive UI and **Prism Laravel package** for connecting into Hermes 3 with Ollama.

---

## Quick summary

**Project name:** TaskLyst
**Description:** Web-based task management for students. Features an AI assistant (Ollama + Hermes 3) that helps prioritize tasks, generate schedules, import Brightspace items, and produce smart reminders and productivity insights.
**Primary tech stack (implementation notes):** Laravel 12 backend, **Livewire 3 components** (UI interactions), Tailwind CSS for styling, **Prism Laravel package** for Hermes 3 + Ollama integration, Brightspace integration for calendar import.

