## Main pages / UI areas

* **Dashboard** — Overview, productivity widgets, AI insights (Livewire 3 components)
* **Tasks** — Daily task list (add/edit/delete, categories, attachments) using Livewire 3 components
* **Calendar** — Weekly (drag-and-drop) + daily/monthly views, sync with Brightspace (Livewire 3-powered)
* **Notifications (Notif)** — In-app and email reminders, AI summaries (Livewire 3 interactive alerts)
