   * Natural-language task creation and prioritization
   * Predictive scheduling based on free slots and user patterns
5. **Notifications**

   * Email + in-app reminders, smart AI-generated summaries
6. **Productivity Insights**

   * Completed vs pending, weekly/monthly trends, AI recommendations
7. **Security & Privacy**

   * Secure authentication, session management
   * Data encryption in transit and at rest (where applicable)
