## API skeleton (example endpoints)

* `POST /api/auth/register` — register student
* `POST /api/auth/login` — login (returns JWT/session)
* `GET /api/tasks` — list tasks (query by date/priority/status)
* `POST /api/tasks` — create task
* `PUT /api/tasks/:id` — update task
* `DELETE /api/tasks/:id` — delete task
* `GET /api/calendar/sync/brightspace` — trigger Brightspace sync
* `POST /api/ai/prompt` — send user message to Ollama/Hermes 3 via **Prism Laravel package**
* `GET /api/insights` — productivity stats
* `POST /api/notifications/send` — send scheduled notifications

